  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854900/extras/741f5fff77bc3b7eb658153de91135df.avif?t=1641887113\" width=357 height=74 /></span><br>G is about a pilot traveling in space with a broken spacecraft.<br>Space pilot G, who travels through the vast universe with a broken AI auto-navigation system, is the best pilot on Earth.<br>Sometimes I avoid meteors with a quick sense and travel using bombs at the right time.<br>Can G, tired of endless travel, find what he wants to find in this vast universe?<br>Be G and find something that G wants to find!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854900/extras/10cb82b08683cedd24a6c65ce512a968.avif?t=1641887113\" width=357 height=74 /></span><br>.G is a game that competes for time by avoiding with arrow keys and WASD and bombs.<br>As time goes by, death approaches in various ways, and the environment only gets harsh!<br>Compete with your friends in local rankings!",
